Titolo: Mystic Heroes

Anno: 2002

Descrizione: Mystic Heroes is a beat 'em up video game developed by Koei. The game is loosely based on Investiture of the Gods, a Chinese supernatural novel about the fall of the Shang Dynasty and the rise of the Zhou Dynasty.
A Game Boy Advance version, known as Magical Hōshin (マジカル封神, Majikaru Hōshin), was released simultaneously with the GameCube version, known as Battle Hōshin (バトル封神, Batoru Hōshin), exclusively in Japan on March 29, 2002. The PlayStation 2 version, known as Chō Battle Hōshin (超・バトル封神, Chō Batoru Hōshin), has additional characters and gameplay modes.

Genere: Non specificato


